oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The great Wilson Dam at Muscle Shoals, Alabama
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Wilson Dam on the Tennessee River.
Construction of Wilson Dam began in 1918 and was completed in 1924. Tennessee Valley Authority (TVA) acquired Wilson Dam in 1933.
